text:
Deja McClendon (born 27 June 1992) is a American volleyball player.
She played at the 2019 FIVB Volleyball Women's Club World Championship.
She played for Penn State University's women's volleyball team, LKS Lodz, Delta Informatica Trentino, and Minas Tênis Clube.
